window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A werewolf killer. A paranormal murder. How many times can Emma Bellamy cheat death? </b></p> <p>I’m one placement away from becoming a fully fledged London detective. It’s bad enough that my last assignment before I qualify is with Supernatural Squad. But that’s nothing compared to what happens next.&nbsp;</p> <p>Brutally murdered by an unknown assailant, I wake up 12 hours later in the morgue - and I’m very much alive. I don’t know how or why it happened. I don’t know who killed me. All I know is that they might try again.&nbsp;</p> <p>Werewolves are disappearing right, left, and centre.&nbsp;</p> <p>A mysterious vampire seems intent on following me everywhere I go.&nbsp;</p> <p>And I have to solve my own vicious killing. Preferably before death comes for me again.</p>"; 
